data.description: Enjoy the opportunity of owning this turn key residence that boasts pride of ownership throughout in a low maintenance serene setting.  New Roof,  New Exterior and New Interior Paint, New Microwave along with an impeccably well kept home makes for the perfect opportunity to just move in , drop your bags and enjoy the lifestyle this cozy cul-de-sac provides.  Centrally located and just minutes from shopping, schools, dining, parks and USA Parkway.  Perfectly matched and ready to move in.
